== Installation (Debian 6 Squeeze) ==
Debian source.list:
deb http://nginx.org/packages/debian/ squeeze nginx
deb-src http://nginx.org/packages/debian/ squeeze nginx

sudo apt-get install nginx python-dev python-mysqldb rubygems openjdk-6-jdk icedtea6-plugin mysql-server mysql-client

http://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools
sudo python setup.py install

sudo easy_install django flup selenium pil simplejson python-memcached pyvirtualdisplay postmarkup pygments django-mediagenerator django-tagging django-celery django-ratings django-social-auth django-profiles django-registration django-debug-toolbar

https://github.com/thornomad/django-hitcount
setup.py install

sudo gem install sass compass
